These streams are related to Collection FrameWorks. These streams are very different
from io stream, io streams are the sequence of data


-> IO Streams are the sequence of data.
Data ko read or write karne ke liye


-> The Stream API are related to Collection Frameworks
When there is group of objects and need to work together so then the Stream API's
are used

These streams are introduced in java 1.8 version.
It basically perform bulk operations and process the objects of Collection.
Reduce the code length


